To ensure equivalent representation of aggregate levels, patch population size can be used to scale mixing coefficients, i.e.. for two patches $i$ and $j$ the mixing coefficient $\phi_{i,j}$:

$$
\phi_{ij} = N_j/N_{tot}
$$

